  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/7b42d972598657f7a697d7b8831175f5.poster.avif?t=1684723658\" width=600 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/7b42d972598657f7a697d7b8831175f5.webm?t=1684723658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/7b42d972598657f7a697d7b8831175f5.mp4?t=1684723658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Pong Pong Crows is a brick breaker game, with bouncing crows and jumping zombies.<br><br>Command your crows flipping up and down, let zombies  go back home!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every launch counts<br></li><li>Nearly every power-up has disadvantages, eat them wisely<br></li><li>Use workshop to extend your experience</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/2b4cd8e23ba75f3f3682813912660c57.poster.avif?t=1684723658\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/2b4cd8e23ba75f3f3682813912660c57.webm?t=1684723658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/2b4cd8e23ba75f3f3682813912660c57.mp4?t=1684723658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Precise bouncing<br></li><li> 18 power-ups<br></li><li> 16 kinds of zombies<br></li><li> 60 stages<br></li><li> Chilling atmosphere<br></li><li> Leaderboards<br></li><li> In game editor and workshop</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/7b42d972598657f7a697d7b8831175f5.poster.avif?t=1684723658\" width=600 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/7b42d972598657f7a697d7b8831175f5.webm?t=1684723658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365220/extras/7b42d972598657f7a697d7b8831175f5.mp4?t=1684723658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
